com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface RedhatLinuxOperatingSystem

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, LinuxOperatingSystem, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OperatingSystem
All Known Implementing Classes:
RedhatLinuxOperatingSystemImpl
public interface RedhatLinuxOperatingSystem
extends LinuxOperatingSystem

A representation of the model object 'Redhat Linux Operating System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Boot Loader
  • Desktop
  • Install Date
  • Last Boot Up Time
  • Owner
  • Product Type
  • SE Linux State

See Also:
OsPackage.getRedhatLinuxOperatingSystem()
